Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.76,0:23:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是煩惱多多的青春花季啊
